    "description": "About Cluely\n\nCluely is building AI to give you an unfair advantage in every situation.\n\nIt acts as a desktop assistant that takes in screen, mic, and audio context to give you information and suggestions that existing model providers cannot, due to a lack of context.\n\nWe will win for two reasons:\n\n1) Chatbots are not the best interface for multi-modal AI\n\n2) We can make anything viral\n\nAbout the Role\n\nWe work six days a week in-person in San Francisco, 10-12 hours a day.\n\nYou are expected to live within a block of the office (housing provided).\n\nOur eng team is a mix of staff-level SWEs and tuff 19 yr olds, check it out here https://www.notion.so/Cluely-Team-1fd73e859d3280eebff2ca7e174078dc?source=copy_link.\n\nYou might be a good fit if you are:\n\n - One of the best engineers in the world\n\n - Down to gamble your life into greatness\n\nCompensation:\n\n - Founding engineers get anywhere from $250-350k base + 0.25-0.5% equity\n\n - We also offer free housing, free food, and free transportation.",
